import {
  Box,
  Card,
  CardBody,
  CardHeader,
  Center,
  Heading,
  Stack,
  StackDivider,
  Text,
  Image,
} from "@chakra-ui/react";
import React from "react";

const Landing = () => {
  return (
    <Center h="100vh" flexDir="column" w="100vw">
      <Card align="center" rounded="2xl" h="xl" w="lg">
        <CardHeader>
          <Center
            flexDir="column"
            gap={5}
            bgGradient="radient(to-b, #white, transparent)"
            backgroundImage="home-ui-bg.svg"
            backgroundPosition="top"
            backgroundSize="inherit"
            h="100vh"
            w="full"
            background="radial-gradient(70% 70% 70% 70% at top, transparent 10%, white 100%), url(/home-ui-bg.svg)"
          >
            <Image
              bg="white"
              alt="logo"
              boxSize="60px"
              shadow="base"
              rounded="lg"
              src="logo192.png"
            />
            <Heading size="md">Welcome</Heading>
          </Center>
        </CardHeader>

        <CardBody>
          <Stack divider={<StackDivider />} spacing="4">
            <Box>
              <Heading size="xs" textTransform="uppercase">
                Summary
              </Heading>
              <Text pt="2" fontSize="sm">
                View a summary of all your clients over the last month.
              </Text>
            </Box>
            <Box>
              <Heading size="xs" textTransform="uppercase">
                Overview
              </Heading>
              <Text pt="2" fontSize="sm">
                Check out the overview of your clients.
              </Text>
            </Box>
            <Box>
              <Heading size="xs" textTransform="uppercase">
                Analysis
              </Heading>
              <Text pt="2" fontSize="sm">
                See a detailed analysis of all your business clients.
              </Text>
            </Box>
          </Stack>
        </CardBody>
      </Card>
    </Center>
  );
};

export default Landing;
